sentence: How many sections of EECS 370 are there ?
sentence-with-vars: How many sections of department0 number0 are there ?
sql: SELECT COUNT( * ) FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 370 AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 = 2070 ;
